  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">I was a Sari(IWAS)-an award-winning sustainable fashion brand- and Fashion in ProcessLab(FiP) at DesignDept. Politecnico di Milano have partnered with CHIME FOR CHANGE to make sustainable fashion impactful.IWAS&apos;s work transforms pre-loved Indian saris into unique style,providing regular income and valuable skills training to vulnerable women in Mumbai.To further IWAS&apos;s work, the brand will engage a DesignResearcher, selected from a global competition, to train and work with the female artisans.</narrative>
  </description>
